---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle="hankadev blog">
  <section
    class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface/75 p-6 sm:p-8"
  >
    <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-accent">
      Outer Rim Dispatch
    </p>
    <h1 class="leading-tight text-primary">I build. I break. I fix.</h1>
    <div class="text-lg text-text leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-6">
      <p>
        A long time ago, in a galaxy far, far away, a child was born - a
        curious, smart, and stubborn girl. She wanted to become the most
        powerful Jedi ever, but unfortunately, she was never tested for her
        midi-chlorian levels. Instead of undergoing Jedi training, she played
        football, ice hockey, and listened to pop punk music. However, she never
        gave up on her dream of becoming a hero, she just needed to find a
        different path.
      </p>
      <p>
        Then one day, her path changed. She was taken in by the Mandalorians -
        warriors who valued skill over destiny and action over intention. They
        taught her their creed: adapt, endure, and finish what you start.
      </p>
      <p>I build. I break. I fix. This is the way.</p>
      <p>
        And so she became a bounty hunter in the galaxy of software engineering,
        taking on contracts with bounties on bugs and glitches. And when the
        work allows it, she writes down her adventures.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="h-px w-full bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-primary/70 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>
    <a
      href="/blog"
      class="mx-auto flex w-fit items-center gap-2 border border-primary/60 px-4 py-2 uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-primary/12 transition-colors"
    >
      Enter the archive
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
